                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-258-victim1427 t18280410-258-viclabel1385"></join>. Hubbard told me, on the 6th of March, that the prisoner had gone off with a boiler - I pursued about 150 yards, and saw him carrying this boiler very leisurely along - I took him back - the boiler had been chained to the door - this is it.</p>
